  "subject": "Enable Tensor Core WMMA for 16x16 GEMM tiles",
  "body": "Nsight Copilot analysis: theoretical lower bound for matrix_mul on RTX 5060 is ~27us with Tensor Cores vs current 50us baseline (CUDA cores only). RTX 5060 supports 4x4x4 FP32 WMMA operations. Implementation: 1) #include <mma.h>, 2) Use wmma::fragment, wmma::load_matrix_sync, wmma::mma_sync, wmma::store_matrix_sync for 16x16x16 tiles, 3) Ensure input matrices are in column-major or row-major as required by WMMA API, 4) Profile with ncu --metrics tensor__core_utilization. Target: reduce from 50us toward 27us. Even 35us would be a 30% improvement.",
